Class HtmlPageAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.api.actions.AbstractAction

          • com.xceptance.xlt.common.actions.HtmlPageAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    URLActionDataExecutionable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XhrHtmlPageAction

    public class HtmlPageAction
extends ModifiedAbstractHtmlPageAction
implements URLActionDataExecutionable
    All it does, is loading a WebResponse for a passed WebRequest. The WebResponse in form of a HtmlPage is wrapped in a URLActionDataExecutableResult. Additionally static content requests are fired and loaded via Downloader.
    Since this class extends ModifiedAbstractHtmlPageAction, the response is parsed into the DOM.
    Author:
    matthias mitterreiter
